        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2011-07-14 11:50:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nThere now seems to be code changes in this patch which was originally opened to simply update some URLs reflecting the Whamcloud maintainership of our Lustre releases.\n\nI just wonder if those changes are relevant to this issue or if they should be in their own issue.  Ultimately, I will leave that decision to you.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "7d3b6df12b9efedce01cb132c38aa554affc9eec",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 147,
        "name": "Maloo",
        "email": "maloo@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2011-07-14 12:42:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/5d656038-ae14-11e0-b33f-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "48f6f87e792d8c38d874402fe9943cb05ac66800",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2011-07-15 09:37:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nBrian, you are probably confused, as I originally was, with changes showing up from other patches that have landed between different revisions of this patch.  This shows up when using the \"Patch History\" feature, since it is comparing the difference between the original patch and the Lustre version ON WHICH THAT PATCH WAS BASED against the new patch against the rebased version of the patch.\n\nTo confirm whether the patch contains those changes or not, you need to compare against the \"base version\" temporarily for that patch.  I just did this and verified the patch contains no changes other than URL updates.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "25b1e594afd472290f9c1b3ff9403c3c2145ee43",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 112,
        "name": "Oleg Drokin",
        "email": "green@whamcloud.com",
